            <div class="subsection-section-head">
              <h3 class="subsection-section-title">What We Believe</h3>
              <div class="subsection-section-description">
                <p>
                  Good design is ethical design. Ethical to our consumers, our material, and our craftsmen. We value
                  empathy for the end user through a focus on functionality, care, and attention to detail. We
                  prioritise sourcing ethically harvested wood, leveraging alternative materials, and minimizing waste.
                  We are also deeply committed to a safe, dignified, and creative workplace for our kaarigars.
                </p>
                <p>
                  The luxury we promise is rooted in our design philosophy. Interacting with furniture is intimate and
                  tactile, which is why we prioritize how people connect with and experience spaces and objects. For us,
                  good design is about creating environments where individuals can express themselves authentically.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
