<section class="section section--pbs-0">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-content">
      <div class="section-body">
        <div class="about-us-highlights">
          <div class="about-us-highlight">
            <div class="about-us-highlight-media">
              <img
                class="about-us-highlight-media-img"
                src="{{ 'u-about-us-highlights-1.jpg' | asset_url }}"
                alt="About us Highlight 1"
                width=""
                height=""
              >
            </div>
            <div class="about-us-highlight-info">
              <div class="about-us-highlight-info-head">
                <h4 class="about-us-highlight-title">Our Team</h4>
              </div>
              <div class="about-us-highlight-text">
                <p>
                  In 2007 our journey began in Zahra's garage with a single carpenter. From at-home exhibitions to our
                  first rented workshop in Kemari, we have steadily grown into a celebrated brand with a global reach.
                  Today our team is made up of over 50 individuals, proudly operating out of a custom-built workshop in
                  Korangi Industrial Area.
                </p>
                <p>
                  We take pride in fostering a community where our employees feel confident and actively participate in
                  decision-making. We credit our growth to our investment in people and delight in each other's personal
                  accomplishments — the mithai tastes all the sweeter when a team member brings in good news!
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="about-us-highlight">
            <div class="about-us-highlight-media">
              <img
                class="about-us-highlight-media-img"
                src="{{ 'u-about-us-highlights-2.jpg' | asset_url }}"
                alt="About us Highlight 2"
                width=""
                height=""
              >
            </div>
            <div class="about-us-highlight-info">
              <div class="about-us-highlight-info-head">
                <h4 class="about-us-highlight-title">Zahra Ebrahim</h4>
                <h6 class="about-us-highlight-subtitle">Founder and Principal</h6>
              </div>
              <div class="about-us-highlight-text">
                <p>
                  Our work can be experienced in some of the country's most prominent spaces — from Islamabad Airport to
                  the Presidential House. Each project is a testament to our attention to detail and our passion for
                  design excellence.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

